gameforge.new_quest_lv52._065_say_reward = "But if I don't get a good night'dormir logo, eu'm[ENTER]going to go crazy. I suppose I have to...[ENTER]But remember that this is for your ears only: I'serei[ENTER]assombrado por quatro fantasmas todas as noites. É que's[ENTER]not the worst of it... I'm responsible for their[ENTER]deaths. "
