gameforge.npc_talk._100_say = "I'm a very old man, but I'm still fit and healthy[ENTER]because I have a special secret. I have found out[ENTER]that a potion made of Gango Root Juice and Tue[ENTER]Fungi can prolong your life. If you want to try[ENTER]the potion, take the ingredients to Yu-Hwan. He[ENTER]can brew the potion for you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._10_say = "Be quiet and maintain your discipline! Behave and[ENTER]don't start any trouble. You should respect your[ENTER]fellow men. Is that understood? "
gameforge.npc_talk._110_npcChat = "Você parece bem forte..."
gameforge.npc_talk._120_say = "Por muitos anos, o segredo da força foi[ENTER]passado em nossa família. Meu pai me disse que,[ENTER]se você misturar a flor-sino na poção da[ENTER]maneira certa, a poção lhe dará força[ENTER]extra por um curto período de tempo. Até onde sei,[ENTER]Beak-Go pode preparar esta poção. Você só precisa[ENTER]trazer uma flor-sino para ele."
gameforge.npc_talk._130_npcChat = "Vá, conte isso na montanha..."
gameforge.npc_talk._140_sayTitle = "Yu-Hwan, o músico:"
gameforge.npc_talk._150_say = "...over the hills and everywhere... Do you also[ENTER]like music? I sing all kinds of songs in solitude[ENTER]here, so that I don't get caught up in the war.[ENTER]But without a country to protect me, I wouldn't[ENTER]be able to keep doing what I do. "
gameforge.npc_talk._160_npcChat = "Por que você lê tanto?"
gameforge.npc_talk._170_sayTitle = "Em breve, o devorador de livros:"
gameforge.npc_talk._180_say = "Oh, aventureiro! O mundo está cheio de problemas.[ENTER]Você só pode sobreviver com uma certa quantidade de[ENTER]conhecimento. Então, honre seus livros. Em tempos ruins -[ENTER]e hoje em dia os tempos são sempre ruins - eles[ENTER]vão ajudar você. Acredite em mim!"
gameforge.npc_talk._190_npcChat = "Você tem filhos?"
gameforge.npc_talk._200_say = "Actually I didn't want any children, but...[ENTER]Well I keep collecting Kaki Blossoms because if[ENTER]you prepare them properly, you can strengthen[ENTER]your magical energy with them. Baek-Go found that[ENTER]out. He only needs a single blossom to make 100[ENTER]potions. Unfortunately the Kaki Blossom also has[ENTER]a side effect. If a woman wears a necklace made[ENTER]from this blossom, she will have a son. Between[ENTER]you and me, my wife shamelessly took advantage of[ENTER]this. "
gameforge.npc_talk._20_npcChat = "Hum, que cheiro bom aqui..."
gameforge.npc_talk._210_npcChat = "What's wrong with your foot? "
gameforge.npc_talk._220_sayTitle = "Handu-Up:"
gameforge.npc_talk._230_say = "It's getting better. While taking a walk[ENTER]recently, I stumbled over a Gango Root and[ENTER]sprained my ankle. Luckily I know the doctor[ENTER]Baek-Go, so he treated me and gave me some[ENTER]advice: To heal small wounds you can brew a[ENTER]potion from these same Gango Roots. So I made the[ENTER]culprit roots into a tea and it cured the damage[ENTER]that it had made... "
gameforge.npc_talk._240_npcChat = "Quem é você?"
gameforge.npc_talk._250_sayTitle = "Wonda-Rim:"
gameforge.npc_talk._260_say = "I am Wonda-Rim, Chaegirab's nephew. My uncle is[ENTER]famous! Do you know him? He experiments a lot[ENTER]with potions and herbs. Whilst doing this, he[ENTER]found out that you can get a large amount of[ENTER]protection against magical energy if you mix 100[ENTER]Bo Water with a Mulberry. As far as I know,[ENTER]Huahn-So can produce the potion if you take the[ENTER]ingredients to him. "
gameforge.npc_talk._270_npcChat = "Por que você tem tantas cicatrizes?"
gameforge.npc_talk._280_sayTitle = "Traidor Balso:"
gameforge.npc_talk._290_say = "I'm not a good fighter and I constantly got hurt[ENTER]in war. At some point I asked Yu-Hwan whether he[ENTER]could brew a potion for me that could protect my[ENTER]body from injuries. He brewed me something from[ENTER]Bellflower Juice and Lilac, but unfortunately the[ENTER]protection wasn'não é suficiente. Ou talvez fosse[ENTER]apenas minha própria incompetência. Mas eu'm sure the potion[ENTER]will help you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._300_npcChat = "Por que tantas pessoas chamam você de traidor?"
gameforge.npc_talk._30_sayTitle = "Octávio, o dono do restaurante:"
gameforge.npc_talk._310_say = "Eu fugi da guerra e me juntei à Gangue do Vento[ENTER]Negro. Meus companheiros nunca me perdoaram por[ENTER]isso. Depois descobri que os Guerreiros do Vento[ENTER]Negro matam pessoas inocentes, então eu[ENTER]imediatamente os deixei. Foi horrível!"
gameforge.npc_talk._320_say = "Você tem pessoas inocentes na sua consciência?[ENTER]Então você realmente merece seu nome. Você os[ENTER]impediu de ter uma boa vida."
gameforge.npc_talk._330_say = "We live in a lawless world. But I have decided[ENTER]that I won't do anything bad any more, ever[ENTER]again. I don't want people to keep describing me[ENTER]as a traitor.[ENTER][ENTER]Have you got some Yang for me? "
gameforge.npc_talk._340_npcChat = "Eles chamam você de estudioso?"
gameforge.npc_talk._350_sayTitle = "Uriel, o Sábio:"
gameforge.npc_talk._360_say = "There are so many things to learn in this vast[ENTER]world. Ignorance paired with military power is an[ENTER]especially dangerous combination. You don't want[ENTER]to live like these ignorant soldiers, right?[ENTER]Knowledge is power! "
gameforge.npc_talk._370_npcChat = "Minhas fontes me dizem que você pratica medicina?"
gameforge.npc_talk._380_say = "I do what I can. But there are more and more[ENTER]casualties every day in this dangerous world. We[ENTER]don't have enough medicine or helpers. Times are[ENTER]hard! Perhaps you could give me a hand later? "
gameforge.npc_talk._390_npcChat = "How's the hunting business going? "
gameforge.npc_talk._400_sayTitle = "Yang-Shin, o Caçador:"
gameforge.npc_talk._40_say = "Bem-vindo! Nosso restaurante tradicional é tão[ENTER]bem-sucedido que poderíamos abrir restaurantes em[ENTER]todo o mundo. Se você quer comer algo delicioso,[ENTER]venha experimentar nossa comida."
gameforge.npc_talk._410_say = "Hmm, ever since the Metin stones came down,[ENTER]animals have become really wild. Nowadays, you're[ENTER]already risking your life when you go out to hunt[ENTER]some chickens. It'é um momento perigoso para os caçadores.[ENTER]Felizmente, eu'm one of the best! "
gameforge.npc_talk._420_npcChat = "De onde vem sua alta precisão?"
gameforge.npc_talk._430_say = "I'm great with a bow, because I have a special[ENTER]recipe, hehe! When you mix Peach Blossom Juice[ENTER]with Lilac, you get a potion that increases your[ENTER]accuracy. Take the ingredients to Yu-Hwan, I'tenho[ENTER]certeza que ele'll brew the potion for you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._440_npcChat = "Que bela guirlanda floral..."
gameforge.npc_talk._450_say = "I used to collect Peach Blossoms with my brother.[ENTER]But I have to do it alone today. They don't look[ENTER]very pretty, but they have a special effect.[ENTER]If you take a Peach Blossom to Baek-Go, he'll[ENTER]brew a potion from it that makes you very[ENTER]nimble-footed! "
gameforge.npc_talk._460_npcChat = "Where's your brother? "
gameforge.npc_talk._470_say = "Recentemente, meu irmão tem viajado muito. Eu[ENTER]mal o vejo mais e me preocupo muito com[ENTER]ele."
gameforge.npc_talk._480_npcChat = "Você vende Bolinhos de Arroz?"
gameforge.npc_talk._490_sayTitle = "Yu-Rang, o(a) vendedor(a) de Bolinhos de Arroz:"
gameforge.npc_talk._500_say = "It is difficult to sell Rice cakes because of the[ENTER]war. Thanks to the bandits, I have lost lots of[ENTER]customers. I just don't know what I should do for[ENTER]a living any more. "
gameforge.npc_talk._50_say = "Embora seja um restaurante grande, a decoração[ENTER]é surpreendentemente simples."
gameforge.npc_talk._510_npcChat = "Quem costuma comprar produtos de você?"
gameforge.npc_talk._520_say = "I sell most of my cakes to travellers. One day, a[ENTER]mysterious cavalier dressed in black came to see[ENTER]me. As payment, he gave me a recipe that you can[ENTER]make with Zin Water. It's a potion that improves[ENTER]your attack power. I sold the recipe to Huahn-So.[ENTER]If you take some Sim Water and an Alpine Rose to[ENTER]Huahn-So, he will produce some Zin-Water for you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._530_npcChat = "Por que você parece tão triste?"
gameforge.npc_talk._540_say = "Ah, quem poderia imaginar que nossos doces sonhos[ENTER]seriam despedaçados tão impiedosamente... Meu pobre[ENTER]marido, ele caiu durante a batalha! ... Por favor, vingue[ENTER]a morte dele."
gameforge.npc_talk._550_npcChat = "Tantas pessoas caíram na guerra..."
gameforge.npc_talk._560_say = "We're losing more and more men in the war, so the[ENTER]women in the village gathered together and asked[ENTER]Huahn-So to create a better healing potion.[ENTER]After a lot of research, he produced a potion[ENTER]which increases defence, so that less healing[ENTER]potions have to be used. Go see him. I'm sure he[ENTER]can produce the potion, that he calls[ENTER]SamBo-Water, for you. He just needs some[ENTER]Dok-Water and a Alpine Rose to make it. "
gameforge.npc_talk._570_npcChat = "Oh, que criança fofa..."
gameforge.npc_talk._580_sayTitle = "Ah-Yu:"
gameforge.npc_talk._590_say = "He is screaming again... I don't know whether he[ENTER]wants some sweets or... oh no! "
gameforge.npc_talk._600_npcChat = "Como vocês dois estão?"
gameforge.npc_talk._60_npcChat = "Fale-me algo sobre cerâmica."
gameforge.npc_talk._610_say = "Meu filho! Agora que meu marido caiu na[ENTER]guerra, preciso me cuidar. Estou tentando[ENTER]sustentar a mim e ao meu filho sozinha. E graças[ENTER]à Água Bo, encontrei uma forma de ganhar a[ENTER]vida. Preciso levar para Yu-Hwan 100 Sucos de[ENTER]Flor Kaki e um Fungo Tue. Ele fabrica a Água Bo[ENTER]com essas coisas, que vende muito facilmente.[ENTER]Afinal, preciso me virar de alguma forma..."
gameforge.npc_talk._620_npcChat = "Como está seu marido?"
gameforge.npc_talk._630_sayTitle = "Aranyo:"
gameforge.npc_talk._640_say = "My so-called husband is married to his books. He[ENTER]barely even looks at me any more. And I'm not an[ENTER]ugly woman. "
gameforge.npc_talk._650_npcChat = "How's business? "
gameforge.npc_talk._660_say = "Since the war broke out, business has been really[ENTER]bad. The merchant's union was once a rich and[ENTER]powerful union, but those days are over now. We[ENTER]cannot keep on ignoring the wild, the white oath[ENTER]soldiers and the black wind soldiers any more. "
gameforge.npc_talk._670_npcChat = "Por que você está de tão mau humor?"
gameforge.npc_talk._680_sayTitle = "Taurean:"
gameforge.npc_talk._690_say = "Harang is a bad girl! I hate her! I'm weak, and[ENTER]she's always picking on me! "
gameforge.npc_talk._700_say = "You're a man, and you have muscles. Work them out[ENTER]a bit! "
gameforge.npc_talk._70_sayTitle = "Yonah, a ceramista:"
gameforge.npc_talk._710_npcChat = "O que você está fazendo?"
gameforge.npc_talk._720_sayTitle = "Harang:"
gameforge.npc_talk._730_say = "I'm waiting for Taurean. We often play together[ENTER]and we fight a lot too. What a coward! If he[ENTER]doesn'Se você não vier voluntariamente, eu'll give him a really[ENTER]hard time! "
gameforge.npc_talk._740_npcChat = "Taurean tem medo de você."
gameforge.npc_talk._750_say = "Taurean is actually stronger than me. So now I've[ENTER]thought of a way that I can win anyway. A white[ENTER]Ninja told me that you can mix Young Water with a[ENTER]Mulberry and make a potion that makes you hit[ENTER]more quickly. Then I'finalmente serei capaz de derrotar[ENTER]Taurean! Se você também quiser se tornar um atacante[ENTER]rápido, então leve os ingredientes para[ENTER]Huahn-So. Eu'm sure he'll make the potion for you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._760_npcChat = "Nova percepção..."
gameforge.npc_talk._770_say_title = "Seon-Pyeong:"
gameforge.npc_talk._780_say = "Meu amigo, o mundo está cheio de perguntas[ENTER]sem resposta. E eu sou um buscador de respostas e[ENTER]um buscador de conhecimento. Você já ouviu falar de[ENTER]armas épicas e Pedras Espirituais?"
gameforge.npc_talk._790_npcChat = "O que você está fazendo?"
gameforge.npc_talk._800_say = "You probably already know that I research unknown[ENTER]knowledge. And at the moment I'm looking into a[ENTER]method of further reinforcing weapons and[ENTER]improving the power of the Spirit Stones. "
gameforge.npc_talk._80_say = "I like being a potter. It's very satisfying to[ENTER]mould clay with your own hands and to see how[ENTER]something is being created... I usually only make[ENTER]simple things. In the east, on the outskirts of[ENTER]the continent, the production methods are a lot[ENTER]more developed. I saw some pottery there once and[ENTER]I was really inspired. Sometimes, when I have the[ENTER]time, I try experimenting. But I still haven't[ENTER]found out which trick they use. "
gameforge.npc_talk._810_npcChat = "A pesquisa de armas..."
gameforge.npc_talk._820_say = "Interesting isn't it? Do you want to know more[ENTER]about it? Then please bring me the appropriate[ENTER]level 65 weapon +9. I also need a Fencing[ENTER]Pamphlet and two Blessing Scrolls. I'll try to[ENTER]make you an epic weapon out of them. "
gameforge.npc_talk._830_say = "However, I can't promise that it'll work. "
gameforge.npc_talk._840_npcChat = "As Pedras Espirituais..."
gameforge.npc_talk._850_say = "Spirit Stones are widely used, but although they[ENTER]are used a lot, most people don't really know[ENTER]what their true power is. But my research has[ENTER]helped me to find out a lot more about them. If[ENTER]you bring me another Spirit Stone, I can improve[ENTER]it for you. "
gameforge.npc_talk._90_npcChat = "You're very sprightly for your age... "
gameforge.olympic_badge = {}
gameforge.olympic_badge._010_npcChat = "Hero's Medal "
gameforge.olympic_badge._020_say = "Me ajude!"
gameforge.olympic_badge._030_say = "Dratted thieves...[ENTER]They broke into my house last night![ENTER]They've stolen the Hero'a Medalha. Meu ancestral foi[ENTER]condecorado com a medalha depois que correu 42,195 km[ENTER]do campo de batalha até seu imperador, para contar[ENTER]a ele sobre a vitória na batalha.[ENTER]E agora's gone! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._040_say = "Ah, meu Deus... isso tem valor sentimental para[ENTER]minha família e eu. O que eu devo fazer?"
gameforge.olympic_badge._050_say = "Você me ajuda?"
gameforge.olympic_badge._060_npcChat = "Hero's Medal "
gameforge.olympic_badge._070_say = "Finally! You're back![ENTER]Did you find the Hero's Medal? "
gameforge.olympic_badge._080_say = "But why? What do those thieves want to do with my[ENTER]medal? It's worthless to strangers! Can you help[ENTER]me find it? "
gameforge.olympic_badge._090_npcChat = "Find the Hero's Medal! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._100_say = "You've returned empty-handed? Oh no, I'estou tão[ENTER]angustiado. Se você puder't help me, then who can?[ENTER]Carry on looking, please! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._110_say = "You've found my medal![ENTER]But wait... that's just one piece of it. What a[ENTER]disgrace, they broke it into five pieces![ENTER]Please bring me all the fragments! Then I might[ENTER]be able to put the medal back together. "
gameforge.olympic_badge._120_say = "Esses criminosos desgraçados quebraram minha herança de[ENTER]família! Obrigado por encontrar todos os pedaços.[ENTER]Agora posso juntar os pedaços novamente."
gameforge.olympic_badge._130_say = "Thank you so much! You've restored my family'é uma[ENTER]honra. Claro que todo o seu esforço não será em[ENTER]vão. Aqui's your just reward! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._140_say = "Do you really want to decline this mission? If[ENTER]you select 'yes', you will not be able to accept[ENTER]it later. "
gameforge.olympic_badge._150_say = "I understand if you don't have enough time for it[ENTER]now. Come again when it suits you better. But[ENTER]don't make me wait for long! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._160_say = "Unfortunately you arrived too late and can't help[ENTER]me now. I wish you all the best for the future! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._170_say = "Hunt the monsters that stole from me! But be[ENTER]careful, they were very strong - at least level[ENTER]30. If you bring back my Hero's Medal, I will[ENTER]give you a generous reward! "
gameforge.olympic_badge._180_say = "Find the Hero's Medal and take it to Yu-Hwan. "
gameforge.olympic_badge._190_say = "Yu-Hwan precisa da sua ajuda. Vá vê-lo! Você o[ENTER]encontrará na segunda vila."
