gameforge.subquest_40._20_say = "Attention warriors! As you can see, the number of[ENTER]attacks made by our enemies is increasing every[ENTER]day. We have also received alarming information[ENTER]from Yu-Hwan. To cut a long story short: We don't[ENTER]have enough arrows! "
