gameforge.subquest_45._130_npcChat = "Os itens do Templo da Escuridão"
gameforge.subquest_45._140_say = "Ah, you've got them! Thank you very much.[ENTER]About the secret people in the temple, well, it'É[ENTER]bem simples: eles're dangerous people.[ENTER]But you'aprenderam isso da maneira mais difícil.[ENTER]Eles também parecem estar servindo aos deuses malignos. Eu[ENTER]não't know any details, but I presume that they[ENTER]are planning something really bad. "
